{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hello there,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the Demo version of Lost In Prayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will find a limited but representative experience of our Traditional Roguelike :\u00a0</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 floors to explore in Hell and Heaven.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">8 fully playable characters with their skill tree.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This demo is a step in our development before launching in Early Access.\u00a0 <br>We know Traditional Roguelikes need a lot of balancing and we want to build the game with you.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join our Discord server or use Steam's forum to give us your feedback.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Lost in Prayer is a turn-based roguelike </strong>true to its roots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expect all the qualities that make the genre so compelling, such as mind-twisting tactical decisions and expansive build options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">High replay value, rewarding progression and tough challenges awaits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Procedurally generated levels ensure no two runs are the same.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore Hell and Heaven each with their dedicated enemies, encounters, and environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique skill trees that offer a variety of playstyles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Loot weapons and armor with dedicated abilities to widen your tactical options.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Permadeath keeps tension high, but if you die\u2026</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>You'll play as your killer!</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138110/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1